description: The Succubus Club has finally returned to Chicago, and there's a party going on. name: One-Shot

description: We travel back and forth in time with Beckett, as he hunts between the lines for a lost treasure.

A Secret Invasion chapter! The Thing and the Human Torch have been blasted into the Negative Zone - and Franklin, Valeria and the entire Baxter Building have come along for the ride! But the biggest surprise is their Skrull enemy: Lyja, the Torch's former wife!

By Roberto Aguirre-Sacasa and Barry Kitson.

Also: the final showdown between the FF and the cosmic-powered Doctor Doom! A classic tale from Stan Lee and Jack Kirby.
name: ﻿The Torch Meets An Old Flame... Lyja!
